name: NotWifGary
description: NotWifGary [$NWG] is a new memecoin launching on Linea, a Layer 2 zkEVM built on Ethereum. With a commitment to a fair launch, the $NWG will be a vanilla ERC20 token, deployed from a multisig wallet involving Original Project Supporters. $NWG symbolizes resistance against regulatory overreach, advocating for #ETHforALL and supporting those in legal battles with U.S. regulators. $NWG champions maximal decentralization from the outset.
